genius.core.uncertainty

Class UncertainPreferenceContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • genius.core.uncertainty.UncertainPreferenceContainer

  • public class UncertainPreferenceContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    Keeps track of both the real preferences of the user as well as the perception of the agent. The preference profile that is given to the agents can be a "distorted utility space" in the cases that uncertainty is included in the form of a perturbation to the real utilities (see AdditiveUtilitySpaceWithPerturbation}) or a flattened Utility Space (see FlattenedUtilitySpace), OR in the form of a Pairwise Comparison User Model (see UserModel). Used only in the core.
